object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct policyreinsurancedetail.SystemId, 
policyreinsurancedetail.ParentId, 
policyreinsurancedetail.CMMContainer, 
policyreinsurancedetail.Id, 
policyreinsurancedetail.GroupIdRef, 
policyreinsurancedetail.GroupIdName, 
policyreinsurancedetail.ReinsuranceTemplateIdRef, 
policyreinsurancedetail.ProbableMaxLoss, 
policyreinsurancedetail.TotalInsuredValue, 
policyreinsurancedetail.PlacementAmt, 
policyreinsurancedetail.StartLimitAmt, 
policyreinsurancedetail.AmtToPlace, 
policyreinsurancedetail.BasePremiumAmt, 
policyreinsurancedetail.PMLOverrideInd, 
policyreinsurancedetail.StatusCd, 
policyreinsurancedetail.BaseWrittenPremiumAmt, 
policyreinsurancedetail.BaseWrittenPremiumToDateAmt, 
policyreinsurancedetail.ManuallyPlacedInd, 
policyreinsurancedetail.CededProRateInd, 
policyreinsurancedetail.Combustability, 
policyreinsurancedetail.FatFryingConducted, 
policyreinsurancedetail.FatFryingAreaPercent, 
policyreinsurancedetail.ProtectionClass, 
policyreinsurancedetail.Construction, 
policyreinsurancedetail.Sprinklered, 
policyreinsurancedetail.ExposureGrade, 
policyreinsurancedetail.StartLimit, 
policyreinsurancedetail.EndLimit, 
policyreinsurancedetail.RowId 
FROM
 policyreinsurancedetail
where systemid in 
(select SystemId from advrxxchangedbeans 
where concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$m_Enddt' 
and cmmcontainer='Policy' ) 
and cmmcontainer='Policy'
